7.BORDERS & OUTLINES

Border aur outline dono element ke around line banate hain, lekin dono me important difference hota hai.

1. BORDER IN CSS

Border element ke content aur margin ke beech me hota hai.

Basic Border Syntax
div{
  border:2px solid black;
}
Breakdown
Part	Meaning
2px	border thickness
solid	border style
black	border color
Border Styles
Solid Border
div{
  border:3px solid red;
}

Straight line.

Dashed Border
div{
  border:3px dashed blue;
}

Broken lines.

Dotted Border
div{
  border:3px dotted green;
}

Dots wali border.

Double Border
div{
  border:5px double black;
}

Double line.

Groove Border
div{
  border:5px groove gray;
}

3D effect.

Individual Side Borders
Top Border
div{
  border-top:4px solid red;
}
Bottom Border
div{
  border-bottom:4px solid blue;
}
Left Border
div{
  border-left:4px solid green;
}
Right Border
div{
  border-right:4px solid black;
}
Border Width
div{
  border-width:5px;
}
Border Color
div{
  border-color:red;
}
Border Radius (VERY IMPORTANT)

Corners ko round karta hai.

6
div{
  border-radius:10px;
}
Circle Banana
img{
  border-radius:50%;
}

Mostly profile pictures me use hota hai.

Different Radius
div{
  border-radius:10px 20px 30px 40px;
}

Order:

top-left
top-right
bottom-right
bottom-left
OUTLINE IN CSS

Outline bhi border jaisi line hoti hai, lekin:

ye border ke bahar hoti hai
layout size affect nahi karti
Basic Outline
div{
  outline:3px solid red;
}
Difference Between Border & Outline
6
Border	Outline
element size affect karta hai	size affect nahi karta
box model ka part hai	box model ka part nahi
har side alag control kar sakte	mostly outside line
rounded ho sakta	radius directly nahi hoti
Outline Offset

Outline aur border ke darmiyan gap.

div{
  border:2px solid black;
  outline:3px solid red;
  outline-offset:10px;
}
Focus Outline

Inputs pe default outline aati hai.

input:focus{
  outline:none;
}
Important Note

outline:none;

Accessibility ke liye carefully use karo, kyunki keyboard users focus outline se navigation samajhte hain.

Better:

input:focus{
  outline:2px solid blue;
}
Border Shorthand
div{
  border:2px solid black;
}

Equivalent to:

div{
  border-width:2px;
  border-style:solid;
  border-color:black;
}
COMPLETE EXAMPLE

HTML:

<div class="box">
  Hello
</div>

CSS:

.box{
  width:200px;
  padding:20px;
  margin:50px;

  border:4px solid black;

  border-radius:15px;

  outline:3px dashed red;

  outline-offset:10px;
}
Real Life Uses
Feature	Use
border	cards, buttons, navbar
border-radius	modern UI
outline	focus effects
outline-offset	stylish effects
